TEST.NOTES:
##ID##
App_CamAlignment_updateYsatOverallExecutionStatus_condition_true_004
##End.ID##
##Description##
Targets true branch of condition ( TeEBA_b_CTScam2maincalibvalid_TRUE == pCalibSave->IaEBA_b_CTScam2maincalibvalid[0u] )
                && 
                ( 
                    ( ( TeEBA_e_CTScam2maincalibtype_SPC == pCalibSave->IeEBA_e_CTScam2maincalibtype )
                    && ( TeEBA_e_COS_camerastate0_INRANGE == pCalibOutputSurr->IeEBA_e_COS_camerastate0 )
                    && ( ( boolean ) TRUE == checkFloatEquality ( 100.0f, pCalibOutputSurr->IeEBA_cnt_COS_camera_CalibrationProgress0 ) )
                    )
                    || 
                    ( ( TeEBA_e_CTScam2maincalibtype_TAC == pCalibSave->IeEBA_e_CTScam2maincalibtype )
                        && ( TeEBA_e_CO_main_safetyState_INRANGE == pcalibOutputProtocol->IeEBA_e_CO_main_safetyState )
                        && ( CALIBRATION_RESULT_READY_PCT == pcalibOutputProtocol->IeEBA_cnt_CO_main_calibrtaion_progress )
                    )
                ).
##End.Description##
##ReviewID##
TBD
##End.ReviewID##
##Status##
Draft
##End.Status##
##Notes##
Intent-only true branch for condition at line 6343.
##End.Notes##
